HEADWORD: Lucernarida
<hw>Lu`cer*nar"i*da</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL.
See <er>Lucernaria</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A
